title: Yes Man
description:
Carl Allen has stumbled across a way to shake free of post-divorce blues and a dead-end job:  embrace life and say yes to everything.  Take a bungee plunge?  Yes.  Accept call-now TV offers?  Yes. Learn Korean?  Yes.  Grab the first flight to anywhere?  Yes.  Win your dream girl?  Yes.  Crack up fans with a feel-good, laugh-loaded romp?  Yes!
